headline: DoorDash, TKO, Williams-Sonoma, Expand Energy will join S&P 500
summary: DoorDash (DASH), TKO Group Holdings (TKO), Williams-Sonoma (WSM), and Expand Energy (EXE) will be part of the S&P 500 (^GSPC) starting on Monday. Yahoo Finance Head of News Myles Udland and Freedom Capital Markets chief global strategist Jay Woods discuss what being included in the index could mean for this group of stocks.
